Standard Chartered May Bid for Nedbank, Times Says

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-04-04T10:56:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/standard-chartered-in-talks-on-nedbank-sunday-times-reports.html
(Corrects headline and story to remove incorrect reference
to companies being in talks. The story was initially published
yesterday.)  Standard Chartered Plc (STAN)  may bid for
 Old Mutual Plc (OML) ’s 52 percent stake in South Africa’s Nedbank
Ltd., Johannesburg’s Sunday Times reported, without saying where
it got the information.  Shaun Gamble, a London-based spokesman for  Standard
Chartered , declined to comment when contacted today by
telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  